usdAaaServerAgent.name: usdAaaServerAgent

revisions.description: Added new B-RAS and accounting objects.
Separated out optional capabilities. Added the subscriber and capabilities groups.
The initial release of this management information module.

usdAaaServerAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdAaaServerAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Authentication, Authorization and Accounting (AAA) Server component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdAaaServerAgentV1.name: usdAaaServerAgentV1
usdAaaServerAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the AAA Server component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version was supported in the Unisphere RX 1.x system
        releases.
usdAaaServerAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the AAA Server application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when new objects were added.

usdAaaServerAgentV2.name: usdAaaServerAgentV2
usdAaaServerAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the AAA Server component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version was supported in the Unisphere RX 2.x system
        releases.
usdAaaServerAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the AAA Server application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when new objects were added and new groupings were defined.

usdAaaServerAgentV3.name: usdAaaServerAgentV3
usdAaaServerAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the AAA Server component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version was supported in the Unisphere RX 3.0 system
        release.
usdAaaServerAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the AAA Server application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the rsAaaAssignDomainStripDomain object was added to the B-RAS group.

usdAaaServerAgentV4.name: usdAaaServerAgentV4
usdAaaServerAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the AAA Server component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version was supported in the Unisphere RX 3.1 system
        release.
usdAaaServerAgentV4.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the AAA Server application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when new assignment delimiter objects were added to the B-RAS group.

usdAaaServerAgentV5.name: usdAaaServerAgentV5
usdAaaServerAgentV5.productrelease:
Version 5 of the AAA Server component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version was supported in the Unisphere RX 3.2 system
        release.
usdAaaServerAgentV5.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the AAA Server application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the groups were separated into multiple statements and the subscriber and capabilties groups were added.
